snippet.title: How to Survive Band Camp 101
snippet.description:
PLAY THE BAND CAMP BOYFRIEND DEMO HERE: https://lovebird-games.itch.io/band-camp-boyfriend
SUPPORT US ON KICKSTARTER: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lovebirdgamestudios/band-camp-boyfriend-marching-band-otome-visual-nov?ref=email
The colorful cast of the upcoming otome visual novel Band Camp Boyfriend is here to help you learn the ropes of marching band in How to Survive Band Camp 101! 

Follow our progress on social media!
Twitter: @Lovebird_Games
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BandCampBoyfriend/
Tumblr: lovebirdgames.tumblr.com
Lemmasoft: https://lemmasoft.renai.us/forums/viewtopic.php?f=43&t=43874

Thanks for checking out our video and have a great day!

---CAST--- (In order of appearance)
Mr. Victor Wiley..................................Mark Coutu
Alex the Bari Saxophonist.................Daisy Guevara
"Poptart" the Mellophonist................Jared Raman
Tom the Trombonist..........................Joe Goffeney
Samuel the Saxophonist....................Devon Kay
Susie the Sousaphonist.....................Emily Woolf
Clark the Clarinetist............................Joe Goffeney
Marian the Marimbist.........................Melody Muze
Garth the Color Guard.........................Joseph Ryan
Felicity the Flutist................................Taylor Burton
Doug the Bass Drummer.....................Richard Barcenas
Sabrina the Color Guard......................Xandra
Aaron the Snare Drummer...................Daniel Acosta
Olive the Mellophonist.........................Lasli Tran
Peter the Trumpeter.............................Jonathan David Bullock
